OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA few mist and fog patches
OL,6,Fpossible at first, but these clearing
OL,7,Fquickly in the morning. Staying dry
OL,8,Fthrough the day with plenty of very
OL,9,Fwarm sunshine and light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry this evening with some
OL,12,Flate evening sunshine. Staying dry and
OL,13,Frather warm tonight with clear skies
OL,14,Facross the region.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FBank holiday Monday will be a
OL,17,Fhot and humid day with plenty of
OL,18,Fstrong sunshine and light winds.
OL,19,FSlightly fresher at the coast with a
OL,20,Fsea breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
