OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying hot, sunny and mostly dry over
OL,7,Fthe next few days. Temperatures
OL,8,Fgradually turning less hot from
OL,9,FWednesday. A little more patchy cloud
OL,10,Fon Thursday, perhaps with the odd
OL,11,Fshower.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
